ation. The web bends to your will now. Onward!"},music:"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/codedex-io.appspot.com/o/audio%2Fcutscenes%2Fhtml%2FRetro%20Boy%20(Full%20Without%20Intro).mp3?alt=media&token=1819cb6b-dd1b-4bd0-94c2-2f8f247f61eb",challengePack:{articleLink:"/challenges/elements/garage-sale",description:"Elements",internalName:"elements-html",internalChallengeLinks:["garage-sale","movie-review","packing-list","map-directions","ramen-restaurant","for-rent"],packXp:65}},{chapterIndex:1,chapterName:"Structure",isClub:!0,chapterDescription:"Learn more about HTML structure, attributes, and classes vs id.",challenges:["Blueprint","Family Tree","Craigslist Ad","Wiki Article","Lorem Ipsum","Power Rangers","MySpace Top 8"],titleImage:"/images/badges/html/structure.png",isComplete:!0,xP:[10,15,15,15,15,20,25],internalChapterName:"structure",internalChallengeNames:["blueprint","family-tree","craigslist-ad","wiki-article","lorem-ipsum","power-rangers","myspace-top-8"],signUpPopups:["blueprint","craigslist-ad"],badgeImage:"/images/badges/html/structure.png",editorState:{blueprint:{enabled:!0},"family-tree":{enabled:!0},"craigslist-ad":{enabled:!0},"wiki-article":{enabled:!0},"lorem-ipsum":{enabled:!0},"power-rangers":{enabled:!0},"myspace-top-8":{enabled:!0}},badgeCardInfo:{imgLink:null,message:"Congrats! You just conjured structure from the void. Wild to think that every website on the internet works this way, right? Let’s keep the magic going."},music:"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/codedex-io.appspot.com/o/audio%2Fcutscenes%2Fhtml%2FRetro%20Boy%20(Stinger).mp3?alt=media&token=67c0494f-4b7f-46dc-ac3c-1812b46a7344",challengePack:{articleLink:"/challenges/structure/song-lyrics",description:"Structure",internalName:"structure-html",internalChallengeLinks:["song-lyrics","metamorphosis","bestie-fan-page","messy-closet","i-spy","juliens-art-mart"],packXp:75}},{chapterIndex:2,chapterName:"Forms",chapterDescription:"Take input from the user with forms.",